    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for that. i guess i'm specifically worried about the part where i have to raise prices or eat the cost. i've heard people argue that raising the wage is basically a way to force small shops out of business to make room for big corporations who can afford it. do you think there's any actual logic to that, or is it just political talk?",
